documentation:
Decodes jsonrpc 2.0 raw message objects into JsonRpcMsg objects.

Examples:
    Request:
        {
            "jsonrpc": "2.0",
            "id": 1,
            "method": "subtract",
            "params": [42, 23]
        }

    Notification:
        {
            "jsonrpc": "2.0",
            "method": "clock",
            "params": "12:00",
        }

    Response:
        {
            "jsonrpc": "2.0",
            "id": 1,
            "result": 0,
        }

    Error:
        {
            "jsonrpc": "2.0",
            "id": 1,
            "error": {
                "code": -32600,
                "message": "Invalid request",
                "data": null
            }
        }
